2:[["$","$L7",null,{"headerBgImage":"/images/articles/news-ai-robot.jpg"}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-page news-article-page","style":{"padding":0},"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","style":{"padding":"0 24px"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"blog-entry-category","children":"20 March 2026"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"Astral 团队加入 OpenAI：Python 工具作者的下一站"}],["$","div",null,{"dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<h3>Astral 是什么来头？</h3>\n<p>Astral 是 Python 生态中最受欢迎的工具库 Ruff 和 uv 的背后团队。Ruff 是一个用 Rust 编写的 Python linter，速度比传统工具快 10-100 倍。uv 则是新一代 Python 包管理器，同样以性能著称。</p>\n\n<h3>为什么加入 OpenAI？</h3>\n<p>据官方公告，Astral 团队将继续推进 Python 开发者工具的创新，同时为 OpenAI 的 AI 编码助手提供技术支持。这是 AI 辅助编程领域的重大信号。</p>\n\n<h3>行业影响</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Python 生态整合</strong>：最优秀的 Python 工具团队进入 AI 领域</li>\n<li><strong>AI 编码加速</strong>：OpenAI 将获得世界顶级的 Python 工具开发能力</li>\n<li><strong>开发者受益</strong>：期待更多 AI 驱动的 Python 开发工具</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>未来展望</h3>\n<p>Astral 团队的加入预示着 AI 公司对开发者工具的重视程度越来越高。Python 作为 AI 领域的首选语言，这次整合将为开发者带来更多惊喜。</p>"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"share-links","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Twitter","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-twitter"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"LinkedIn","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-linkedin-in"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Facebook","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-facebook-f"}]}]]}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-light pt-4 pb-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h3",null,{"style":{"marginBottom":"24px","fontSize":"18px","fontWeight":700},"children":"其他新闻"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"posts-grid","children":[["$","div","google-android-sideload",{"className":"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4 blog-item","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"card h-100","children":["$","$L8"